~~~~~~~~~~~
Timetra PIM
~~~~~~~~~~~

A Personal Information Tracker with YAML backend + CLI frontend.

Shares ideology with `Timetra Diary`_.

"Timetra" is an umbrella project for a set of PIM-related tools.
